description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Potomac, which features the women in Portugal and Michael still Michael'ing back in Potomac. On The Bachelorette, Clare and Dale finally get their romaine lettuce happy ending and Tayshia arrives at La Quinta.


The Bachelorette Recap: 23:20ish


PS Subscribe to Danny's spinoff podcast, A Very Merry Iconic Podcast, which is out now!
